Necessary changes to mp4parser source code to read the art cover and
custom box parsing.

MP4Muxer using new mp4parser source code.
Patch to AppleCoverBox.
Fixed cast error reported in play.
initial update to integrate ocm-lockscreen update
Fixes crash on android-15 (4.0.3) when playing a ringtone, reported by Amazon Android Store QA Team, thanks\!
Update on UserAgents, updated list and an initial shuffle when the classloader instantiates the static list.
Avoids crash on devices that don't have the android market installed.
removing layout animation transition from transfer fragments, this was the cause why the layout wasn't being rendered correctly on startup (when the user didn't have an sd card to chose from)
Now recommending Mycelium wallet, much friendlier backup and *restore* mechanism than schildbach's. If user has no market app installed, we open the website of the mycelium wallet.

enable no bitcoin wallet available screen for kindle. refactor. still not a single bitcoin wallet on the amazon app store, so sending users to mycelium webpage (wallet works on kindle, tested it), small refactor.
handle new soundcloud 302 json responses, was breaking url downloads.
soundcloud downloads by url are back. refactor.
chinese translation folder had the wrong local name all along.
added a community translation framework/tool for users to help us (Transcommu)
Better error handling and regex in extract_function.
Initial support for object definition parsing.

Fix slice.
Implement splice and general improvement.
'reverse' modifies the array in place.
Using list in for better mutability.
don't leave downloadUrl null when both video and audio urls are available.
